@startuml
title [Pattern 3] Voice Integrated Orchestration Sequence (A2A Standard)

skinparam sequence {
    ArrowColor #3B82F6
    LifeLineBorderColor #3B82F6
    ParticipantBorderColor #3B82F6
    BackgroundColor #F8FAFC
}

participant "User / Browser" as User
participant "UI (voice.js/app.js)" as UI
participant "Supervisor API\n(FastAPI)" as API
participant "Agent Service\n(Orchestrator)" as Agent
participant "OpenAI Realtime API\n(WSS)" as OpenAI

== 1. Session Initialization ==

User -> UI : 마이크 버튼 클릭
activate UI
UI -> API : WS Connection /a2a/supervisor/voice/stream?session_id=UUID
activate API

API -> OpenAI : WSS Connection (PCM16, 24kHz)
OpenAI --> API : Session Started
API -> OpenAI : session.update (stt-system prompt)
API --> UI : WebSocket Accept

== 2. Audio Streaming & Real-time Transcription ==

loop Voice Activity
    User -> UI : 음성 입력 (Voice Speaking)
    UI -> API : Binary (Audio Chunks)
    API -> OpenAI : input_audio_buffer.append
    
    OpenAI --> API : response.text.delta (Real-time Echo)
    API --> UI : { "type": "transcript", "text": "..." }
    UI -> UI : Overlay 업데이트
end

== 3. Server-Side Integrated Orchestration (Pattern 3) ==

OpenAI --> API : input_audio_transcription.completed (Final Text)
activate API #LightBlue

note right of API: 서버가 직접 태스크 트리거 (패턴 3)
API -> Agent : execute_task(session_id, transcript, request_id)
activate Agent
Agent -> Agent : Task Created (Accepted/Streaming)
Agent --> API : { "task_id": "T-123", "status": "STREAMING" }
deactivate Agent

API --> UI : { "type": "final_transcript", "text": "...", "task_started": true, "task_id": "T-123" }
deactivate API

== 4. Seamless SSE Subscription ==

UI -> UI : stopVoice() & UI 전환
UI -> API : POST /a2a/supervisor/stream (SSE Subscription for T-123)
activate API

loop Task Execution Events
    Agent -> API : Event (analyzing/planning/invoking...)
    API --> UI : SSE Event (progress/chunk/reasoning)
    UI -> UI : Chat Bubble & Progress 업데이트
end

API --> UI : SSE Event (done)
deactivate API

@enduml
